Opie & Jim Norton OCT 29 2015 Thu (02:55:45)


On Today's Show:

MARK NORMAND & KAITLYN FARRINGTON.


They talk about a nude pic of Dane Cook and then they cover last night's Presidential debate with their old pal "Stuntbrain" on the phone.

Mark Normand joins them. They talk about women having vagina surgery and Kaitlyn Farrington joins them. They talk about some of her adventures and things that she can't do anymore because of spinal problems.

They talk about her gold medal and other Olympics stuff, wolves, and a bunch of news stories
